   AETNA LIFE &amp; CASUALTY Co. (Hartford, Conn.) -- Zoe Baird
was named vice president and general counsel of this
multi-line insurance company, effective July 16. Ms. Baird,
37 years old, succeeds Stephen B. Middlebrook, who has been
